{"note_id": "69b52e7e000000001a0202b8", "title": "上海徐汇区City Walk", "desc": "闲逛路线：徐家汇地铁站出→徐家汇书院→徐家汇天主教堂→美罗城→徐家汇公园→吴兴公园→武康大楼\n📍标志性地点：\nP2-P5，三楼阳台视角很好，可以拍教堂；最近有白瓷展，P5的《赤道南北两总星图》我想称其为桃源观星攻略。\nP6-P7，美罗城与书院隔一条马路，不想过马路的话可以从地铁口到地下过。美罗城的橡子共和国，超多可爱的龙猫。\nP8，去往徐家汇公园的过街天桥上 ，两边都是郁金香。\nP9—P12，徐家汇公园，玉兰花，郁金香开得很好。P12点位在百代小楼出口旁边，晴天下午的郁金香好像在发光。\nP13，吴兴公园，坐在长椅上吹吹风很惬意。\nP14-15，永康大楼，人巨多，想顺路逛逛淮海中路的话可以去看看。\n#春天就要逛公园[话题]# #上海citywalk[话题]# #周末去哪儿[话题]# #逛吃逛吃[话题]#", "type": "normal", "time": 1773481598000, "author": {"user_id": "5edc981d0000000001004e8a", "nickname": "🔆"}, "interact_info": {"liked_count": "77", "comment_count": "2", "collected_count": "76", "shared_count": ""}, "image_urls": ["http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061738/78fd8822a5e30183c9d57b75b77948bb/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031tmk4q9jmu605nmsj0eg8jka0rs7098!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3", "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061738/7a643ab50bc39f44ffb754e2dc4e6df7/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031tmk4rdo6ub05nmsj0eg8jkah55e1ng!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3", "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061738/e74d9ad3e132602796c1320629aedac4/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031tmk4rdo6ucg5nmsj0eg8jka5e83ujg!nd_dft_wgth_webp_3", "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061738/138a018fea9cf0cfacf943a4cedb6ba5/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031tmk4q9jmu1g5nmsj0eg8jka20gnv9o!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3", "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061738/0ef9579265cd07507a242fb32b63e5ca/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031tmk4q9jmu4g5nmsj0eg8jka0619g58!nd_dft_wgth_webp_3", "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061738/f0851c7567b4672ddaf4d7d522637247/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031tmk4q9jmu105nmsj0eg8jka6nmjh2g!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3", "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061738/d9116aca8698a786e4efc5db05fbba24/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031tmk4q9jmu0g5nmsj0eg8jkadhvnl0g!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3", "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061738/346b8b9d3d85a4d5031c83549c8fe283/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031tmk4q9jmu205nmsj0eg8jkacirnc28!nd_dft_wgth_webp_3", "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061738/727eefea8386a3005a385f52c7bf